@@$TJvCaretEdit
<GROUP JVCL.Edits>
<TITLE TJvCaretEdit overview>
  TJvCaretEdit is a TEdit descendant that provides custom caret shapes. There are two types of
  carets that can be generated: a caret of custom width and height (optionally grayed) or a bitmap
  caret.

  To use an edit with custom caret execute the following tasks:

  * Drop a TJvCaretEdit on a form.
  * Specify the <LINK TJvCaretEdit.Caret, caret settings>.
